<i>tělo se třese.</i>

102
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:55,840
Hej, Shigo!

103
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:57,520
Ty máš teda kuráž!

104
00:11:57,560 --> 00:12:00,080
Co se děje?

105
