252
00:34:15,560 --> 00:34:17,720
Zadrž, matko!

253
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:21,040
Toto je konec klanu Shiga!

254
00:34:23,040 --> 00:34:26,600
Ne, budu Yuzurovou manželkou!

